<h1 id="course-creation-guidelines-by-10pearls-university">Course Creation Guidelines by 10Pearls University</h1>
<p><strong>Welcome on board!</strong></p>
<p>10Pearls University is super excited to collaborate with you over launching a course for our E-learning portal! This isn’t just a collaboration, it’s a celebration of knowledge and expertise! Here are some guidelines that you should consider when creating the course.</p>
<h2 id="lesson-plan-phase-2-days">Lesson Plan Phase (2 days):</h2>
<ul>
<li>Begin with the blueprint for your course.</li>
<li>Share it on the designated SharePoint folder.</li>
<li>Await your technical mentor’s approval.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="content-phase-5-days">Content Phase (5 days):</h2>
<ul>
<li>Craft dynamic PowerPoint presentations following the template.</li>
<li>If necessary, create content scripts (within 1 day) and ensure alignment with your lesson plan.</li>
<li>Safeguard all course elements by uploading scripts and presentations to the course directory.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="loom-recording-phase-15-days">Loom Recording Phase (15 days):</h2>
<ul>
<li>Focus on recordings using LOOM.</li>
<li>Record bite-sized video modules, with each segment not exceeding 8 minutes.</li>
<li>Maintain an active webcam, while ensuring the on-screen timer is off.</li>
<li>Keep the team informed about any hardware or software needs.</li>
<li>Submit recorded videos for thorough review.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="physical-shoots">Physical Shoots:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Consider physical shoots for in-depth content, including Intro and Outro videos.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="editing-phase">Editing Phase:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Build the course landing page and quizzes within 3 days, while the editing team enhances your video recordings.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="course-launch">Course Launch:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Witness your course coming to life on the 10Pearls portal.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="marketing-phase">Marketing Phase:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Prepare for an exciting course promotion by the marketing team across various social media platforms.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="payment">Payment:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Celebrate your hard work as payment is sent to your provided bank account.</li>
</ul>
<p>As we bring the course creation journey at 10Pearls University to a close, our excitement for the upcoming collaboration is off the charts, and we can’t wait for you to join in the thrill!</p>
<p>Throughout the course development journey, rest assured that the 10PU team will stand by your side, providing guidance and support every step of the way. We’re dedicated to facilitating your course creation experience, and ensuring your success is our top priority.</p>
<p>Thank you for embarking on this thrilling collaboration with 10Pearls University!</p>

